<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>My GitHub Pages Site</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="A simple website hosted with GitHub Pages." />

  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #050816;
      color: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1f2937, #020617);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2.25rem;
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.15);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.18), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.16), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
    }
    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .pill-dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, #38bdf8, #a855f7, #f97316);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
      text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35);
    }
    p {
      color: #cbd5f5;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
      max-width: 34rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .meta span {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .btn {
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.12s ease, background 0.12s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      color: #0b1120;
      box-shadow:
        0 12px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.55),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow:
        0 16px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.7),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    }
    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 1);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .card { padding: 1.9rem 1.5rem; }
      .buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
      .btn { justify-content: center; width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <div class="glow"></div>

    <div class="pill">
      <span class="pill-dot"></span>
      <span>Live on GitHub Pages</span>
    </div>

    <h1>
      Hey, I’m <span>Your Name</span><br />
      and this site runs from a Git commit.
    </h1>

    <p>
      This page is just a simple HTML file pushed to a GitHub repository and
      published with GitHub Pages. Every time I commit and push, the site
      updates—no servers, no deploy scripts, just Git.
    </p>

    <div class="meta">
      <span>GitHub Pages</span>
      <span>Static HTML + CSS</span>
      <span>Versioned by Git</span>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/your-username/your-repo" target="_blank">
        View the code on GitHub
      </a>

      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://your-username.github.io/your-repo" target="_blank">
        Open the live site
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

